- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper uses visual information for the manipulation tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses learning and generalisation in robots. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with control networks for robot manipulation tasks.
